WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:04.540 --> 00:00:09.080
Crochet flower bookmark

00:00:09.680 --> 00:00:13.840
This bookmark is made with a tiny flowers, a long chain and a flower bud

00:00:14.320 --> 00:00:21.160
We use this bookmark as a present with our business Cards

00:00:21.800 --> 00:00:25.680
We wind the flower bookmark around the card!

00:00:52.760 --> 00:00:56.440
What do you need?

00:00:58.020 --> 00:01:02.140
Crochet cotton yarn

00:01:04.280 --> 00:01:08.020
Crochet hook size US No.0 (1.75 mm)

00:01:09.720 --> 00:01:14.100
Scissors

00:01:16.380 --> 00:01:20.440
Yarn needle

00:01:22.460 --> 00:01:25.860
Let's begin...

00:01:27.480 --> 00:01:40.380
Only for this video we'll use thicker crochet and yarn

00:01:43.660 --> 00:01:47.680
Working the flower center

00:01:49.620 --> 00:01:55.000
Work 5 single crochet in a magic adjustable ring

00:01:56.980 --> 00:02:08.680
Begin with 1 chain and then work the 5 single crochet stitches

00:02:10.720 --> 00:02:14.920
Finish closing the adjustable ring,

00:02:15.980 --> 00:02:20.660
and join with a slip stitch

00:02:22.500 --> 00:02:25.220
Working the steam (long chain)

00:02:26.100 --> 00:02:29.020
Chain 85

00:02:29.980 --> 00:02:33.280
You can work some more or less chains

00:02:36.020 --> 00:02:40.140
Cut yarn,

00:02:43.100 --> 00:02:48.320
yarn over and pull it through the last chain

00:02:54.240 --> 00:02:58.840
Working the petals

00:02:59.900 --> 00:03:03.760
Join other color (yellow) and repeat from * to *

00:03:04.960 --> 00:03:32.100
*4 half double crochet in the same chain,

00:03:32.760 --> 00:03:37.920
finish with a slip stitch in the next chain*

00:03:38.580 --> 00:03:42.860
Repeat from * to * all around

00:03:44.380 --> 00:04:09.980
Remember: repeat *4 half double crochet in the same chain, 1 slip stitch in the next chain*

00:04:16.100 --> 00:04:16.600

00:04:16.600 --> 00:04:22.400
To finish the last petal work a slip stitch in the 1st chain

00:04:23.040 --> 00:04:26.600
(Where you worked the 1st stitch)

00:04:29.020 --> 00:04:35.660
Cut yarn an weave the tail through the stitches of the fabric to hide it.

00:04:36.820 --> 00:04:41.020
Cut the other yarn tails too

00:04:45.680 --> 00:04:48.840
Working the flower bud

00:04:49.640 --> 00:04:55.100
Attach the yarn in the last chain of stem

00:04:58.720 --> 00:05:26.040
Work 5 half double crochet in the same chain

00:05:28.140 --> 00:05:36.880
Cut yarn an weave the tail through the stitches of the fabric to hide it.

00:05:37.799 --> 00:05:40.279
We've finished the flower bookmark

00:05:40.660 --> 00:05:44.740
We made it with the cotton yarn and the No. 1 crochet hook

00:05:46.300 --> 00:05:50.820
To wrap it around the business card

00:05:51.260 --> 00:05:53.820
place the flower in front

00:05:54.420 --> 00:05:58.340
wind the chain to the back side

00:05:59.000 --> 00:06:01.800
wrap the flower

00:06:03.100 --> 00:06:07.840
wind the chain to the back side again

00:06:09.260 --> 00:06:18.100
To finish pass the flower through the two chain in front side

00:06:22.340 --> 00:06:28.340
To use this flower as  book mark

00:06:29.460 --> 00:06:37.240
place the chain between the pages you want to mark

00:06:39.340 --> 00:06:44.860
And now you can bookmark the page where you stayed!

